data.description: Located in highly rated Minooka Schools! As you walk under the covered porch you will feel at home. The spacious lower level offers a separate dining room, powder room, laundry room, family room and kitchen with adjacent breakfast room. The kitchen has an upgraded kitchen island, granite counters and stainless steel appliances will stay with the home. The dishwasher is new. Upstairs there are four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary bedroom is a generous 13x16. The primary bathroom has a separate water closet, double sinks, garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet. The partial basement is ready for your finishes. The concrete crawl space has tons of room for storage. The large fully fenced yard features wooden deck and above ground pool. The backyard has added privacy with mature trees and backs to a farm field. There is a transferable 30 year structural warranty. The roof was replaced in  February of 2023. Original owners. Don't miss out on this beautiful home.
